{"title":"Linux宿主机与主机通信","slug":"linux_ping","date":"2018-04-27T02:39:50.419Z","updated":"2018-04-27T02:39:50.615Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/linux_ping.json","photos":[],"link":"","excerpt":"这就是你ping不通的原因","covers":null,"content":"<p>这就是你ping不通的原因</p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<h3 id=\"虚拟机的方式设置为桥接模式。\"><a href=\"#虚拟机的方式设置为桥接模式。\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"虚拟机的方式设置为桥接模式。\"></a>虚拟机的方式设置为桥接模式。</h3><p>在linux宿主机里配置，在文件系统里找到/etc/network下的interfaces文件打开修改或者打开终端输入</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">root@Crazy:~<span class=\"comment\"># vi /etc/network/interfaces</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>打开后在后面添加</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">auto eth0</span><br><span class=\"line\">iface eth0 inet static  //配置eth0使用默认的静态地址</span><br><span class=\"line\">address 192.168.56.100    //设置eth0的IP地址</span><br><span class=\"line\">netmask 255.255.255.0     //配置eth0的子网掩码</span><br><span class=\"line\">gateway 192.168.56.1    //使用主机的默认网关</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>重启网卡</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">root@Crazy:~<span class=\"comment\"># /etc/init.d/networking restart</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>ping测试是否可以进行通信</p>\n","categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"Linux,网络","slug":"Linux-网络","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Linux-网络.json"}]}